  "detailed_description": "<strong>Sort the Cube</strong> is a minimalistic puzzle game in which you have to arrange all the sides of a cube in the proper order by sliding around the little pieces that make up the cube into the blank spot.<br><br>The game features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Several cube sizes<br></li><li>A couple of images<br></li><li>Selectable shuffling</li></ul><br>So prepare yourself and start putting those little cubes into their places. And don’t forget that the cube has six sides.",
